          <p><span class="status-green">‚óè Live</span> at <a href="https://qrltt.com">qrltt.com</a></p>
          <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <span class="tag">Astro</span>
            <span class="tag">Cloudflare Pages</span>
            <span class="tag">Git/GitHub</span>
            <span class="tag">CI/CD</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Local Homelab Environment</h3>
          <p>Running Ubuntu Server on local hardware. Exposed securely via Cloudflare Zero Trust Tunnels (No open ports).</p>
          <p><span class="status-green">‚óè Operational</span></p>
          <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <span class="tag">Ubuntu Server</span>
            <span class="tag">Docker</span>
            <span class="tag">Cloudflare Tunnels</span>
            <span class="tag">SSH</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Project Y11: Modernization</h3>
          <p>Restoring and upgrading a 2001 Nissan Y11. Blending mechanical restoration with modern tech.</p>
          <p><span class="status-yellow">‚óè Phase 2</span>: <em>Head Gasket & Cooling System Overhaul</em></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
