        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cloud & Networking:</strong> DNS Management, Cloudflare Zero Trust, iCloud+ Custom Domains, Firewall Rules.</li>
          <li><strong>Systems:</strong> Debian/Ubuntu Linux, Bash Scripting, Package Management.</li>
          <li><strong>Web:</strong> HTML5, CSS3, Astro Framework, Static Site Generation (SSG).</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <footer>
        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #333;" />
        <p>¬© 2025 QRLTT | <a href="mailto:me@qrltt.com">Contact Me</a></p>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
